{"tid":47400,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"science 奮鬥之旅","createTime":"2016-12-20T10:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T12:41:25.000Z","uid":3775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dfb6ce420563e41262e36fa3364a40516b1c939","tid":47400,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"想當年 覺得解到一條數好有成功感 好似解開左puzzle<br />\n<br />\n想當年計phy題目好有趣 跳水 接觸水面一刻既加速度會係幾多<br />\n<br />\n想當年讀生物 各大system都背到熟一熟 尤其diabetes 既成因 有一刻會覺得自己做到醫生<br />\n<br />\n想當年讀化學 上有orbital 下有organic chem 以為自己乜都可以synthesis <br />\n<br />\n但係呢 屙篤尿 照下鏡 碌左入science <br />\n<br />\n好彩我夠大志 最後一年考左保安牌 有工返<br />\n都有12000 <br />\n<br />\n30年唔洗錢都上到樓既 50歲啦 （無通脹既話）<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSci仔 考左保安牌未啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa990a59854b24fae42f4fdaa2ed86ca3227f5d","tid":47400,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"哂銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875ce08bbbf4a06b0e3452111bd273972146795e","tid":47400,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哂銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得考牌<br />\n唔係無工返架"},{"pid":"cecdb687f16008337df7e655bf501387dda4da68","tid":47400,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"不要再說了<br />\n下年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8f6f4a20101edbf98ddd2fc0839f9fb5635293","tid":47400,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不要再說了<br />\n下年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得考牌 有樓有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6abbd5e645d21cab8e0b9b2dcd8fdc84e2ce5dd","tid":47400,"u